verbose_text: We discovered that the SPIO deposition in the SD-MBs + FUS + MT group was 2.8 fold higher than that of the SD-MBs + FUS group, indicating that SPIO deposition can be enhanced by MT (with MT : 36.1 +/- 4.2 mug/g tissue; without MT : 13.3 +/- 4.1 mug/g tissue).
evidence: SPIO deposition can be enhanced by MT
